                <note rend="inline" type="source">811.2300/1: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Denmark</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Prince</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Copenhagen</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1923-08-01T17:00:00+01:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 1, 1923—5 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received August 1—1:53 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>26. Department’s telegram 20, July 17, 2 p.m. Danish Foreign Office informs me
                    that Icelandic Government has granted permission for proposed investigation by
                    War Department.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Prince</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
